Revision history for Perl extension Astro::FITS::CFITSIO::CheckStatus.


0.03  Mon Apr  5 11:49:03 EDT 2004	
      - the status variable can be used to provide an additional error
        message to be reported.

      - more class methods available, e.g. to change croak method
		
0.02  Fri Mar 12 11:00:39 EST 2004
      - added documentation(!), ability to provide a user specified
	subroutine to call instead of Carp::croak, so can use
        e.g. Log::Log4perl's logcroak

0.01  Mon Jul 28 10:37:10 2003
      - original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
	-AXc -n Astro::FITS::CFITSIO::CheckStatus

